value:
HAPPY NEW YEAR! Feels nice to just
yell sometimes, right? I definitely feel
safer knowing I can call for help.

In my world, we didn't have the time
to celebrate the new year. It took
everything we had just to survive...

The year of the rabbit in your world
is once every twelve years, right?
That's a lot of years...

This kimono is nice and all, but it's
kind of hard to move around in. What
if someone attacks me?

Mother really looks good in a kimono!
So confident and beautiful... I'm proud
to be her son.

Hey there! I've got a New Year's gift
and well wishes for you from your
friend $Nf.

Not sure why, but I'm feeling really
good this year! At this rate, I'll be
safe from extinction!

W-well, the year has only just begun.
It's OK to take it slow and steady.

Oh, no... This is really, really bad.
Sorry, Mother, I couldn't save the
taguel from extinction...

This'll be perfect for avoiding any
danger! ...That is what it's for, right?

My name is Yarne. I've heard that this
is the year of the rabbit, so I'll try to
keep a hop in my step all year.

Something about a new year just
makes me want to jump around.
Like, boing!$k$pAfter all, a new year means I survived
the last one! So here's hoping nothing
bad happens this year either.$k$pIt's not all bad to go in blind, though.
Otherwise, I wouldn't be so excited
right now.$k$pThat said, I can't be careless! A rash
taguel can meet their end in the blink
of an eye!$k$pBut I'm going to survive this year,
along with Mother. Side by side, as
mother and son.$k$pNeedless to say, I'll be counting on
you, $Nu!
Happy New Year!
Let's celebrate!
I'm not dying this year!
I'll hop circles around you!
I can't go extinct...
A new year has begun! Let's make it a good one, OK?
Ah! Hey, watch it! These ears are off limits!
There's a "Year of the Rabbit" in your world? *gasp* Rabbits get a whole year?
My Anti-Extinction Exercise Program is the perfect way to start the year on the right foot! One, two, one, two...
Oh, this? It's a talisman meant to ward off extinction.
*sniffle* Check it outâ€”Mother gave me a New Year's gift!
You know, it's scary not knowing what the new year might bring...but I'm still gonna give it my all!
Got it!
Err... Which way?
Off to a great start!
